{
  "stem": "23428.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So-- so the lead-- the kapos and the Lageralteste-- the-- the chief of the-- of the-- of the compound-- stood in front of you, like-- like the officers in the army and counted you.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Gave a report-- 693 men here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And actually, we had to stand at attention, with our hats off.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And 46 in the sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that adds up to whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so people could do their counting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "See, but these nightly occasions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was-- became, of course, very obvious what the rank differences were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so, I remember some of the-- in particular, two chieftains of the compound, one a German communist and the other a Russian general, you know, who moved [? with us, ?] they were absolutely safe.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Nothing-- you know, they could have survived concentration camp for 10 years, which obviously, the communists did.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Well, they obviously had locked them up at the latest, after the Spanish civil war in '36.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So he had been there for eight years, and nothing to worry about.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And to make it worse, you have these guys in front of the other prisoners, showing off their wealth, I remember.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There were SS people actually present in the nightly appell because the-- the-- the number of people involved were-- again, at attention-- were communicated to the governing SS people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But not only this, but the-- the-- the communist prisoner nightly pulled out a golden-- golden cigarette case and offered the SS his cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, these guys had everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had servants.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had children working for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, people felt-- that may or may not be the case they were all pedophiles.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I-- I doubt that they're all pedophiles, but probably some of them.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
